{"tid":1515820,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動PO] 928 香城Online: 新政府成立日","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T11:24:33.000Z","uid":260988,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1d0e6401b4368cdd2952950725abbccdb56c87","tid":1515820,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間：9月28日正午12時<br />\n地點：香城Online 和平紀念碑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>啟動香城民意授權大會：</strong></span></span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宣佈新香城政府成立</span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宣佈否定黑港政府，將黑港政權列為非法組織</span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宣佈否定黑港警隊，將黑港警隊列為非法組織</span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宣佈否定黑港法律，廢除黑港法律</span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">成立公民保衛隊，授權全民於香城Online以武制暴，對付反對份子</span><br />\n- 民意授權，<span style=\"color: orange;\">撥款聘請各國聯軍助守</span>"},{"pid":"1f3a08d150df71eae6f730c3c3874148cc4d054e","tid":1515820,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0130b7229b3f2bea9dce6dfe1628ef3508f65396","tid":1515820,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3a08d150df71eae6f730c3c3874148cc4d054e","tid":1515820,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04507fc5a7d8c0500614b382329e52bc19412d3c","tid":1515820,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"新手上路"},{"pid":"845838405cb6732e14758a978df46e303436654a","tid":1515820,"uid":4618,"like":0,"disli